# .viewerignore — gitignore-syntax exclude list applied WITHIN each content
# root declared in viewer.content.json (Plan: multi-root viewer content).
#
# The built-in defaults (node_modules/ archive/ .viewer-highlights/ dist/
# download/ temp/ .git/ viewer/) are always applied and need not be repeated
# here. The reader-prose roots are curated, so this file only needs to prune
# any incidental non-reader artifacts that land inside a root.

# Scratch / backup files anywhere in a root.
**/*.scratch.md
**/*.bak.md
